A Blowout Halloween Bash

Demi Lovato threw an epic Halloween party on Saturday night, complete with an A-list guest list and a Marie Antoinette inspired costume. Halloween brings out the creative in everyone, and Lovato did not disappoint with her bash at the Hyde Lounge in West Hollywood.

A Bump Along The Way

One of her guests was Kylie Jenner, and unfortunately for Jenner, she hit a bit of a speed bump on the way to the party. Or rather, she hit another car on the way to the party. Her driver backed into another vehicle on the way to the party -- Jenner was in the back seat during the accident.

Fight For Your Right To Party

Luckily, the accident didn't ruin her night, and she was able to party the night away in her Madonna costume. She even reenacted the infamous Madonna-Britney kiss with her best friend Anastasia “Stassie” Karanikolaou. All's well that ends well!
description: A pitstop on the way to the bash.
